Description: fullscreen desktop, Fixed FBO, resizable window
 Claude : All the scene is rendered in a 640x480 FBO (Original demo resolution).
 At the end of each frame, the FBO is blitted to the default framebuffer using 
 glBlitFramebuffer(), maintaining the 4:3 aspect ratio 
 (black pillarbox/letterbox bars if necessary).
 The glCopyTexSubImage2D() function of the "shine" effect reads from the linked 
 FBO, so the visual behavior is identical to the original.
